Okay, I need to match order forms with invoices and record the information. I will start by selecting the first order and invoice, then click the "match" button, and finally click the "record" button.
```json
<OUTPUT_JSON>[
  {"action": "click", "selector": "table:has-text(\"order\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]", "text": ""},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "table:has-text(\"invoice\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]", "text": ""},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"match\" i)", "text": ""},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"record\" i)", "text": ""}
]</OUTPUT_JSON>
```
